replies.body:
I know this will probably sound utterly ridiculous, Is it possible to bring in banners for people that do certain negative actions? So we have teamwork and honourable opponent, why not have uncooperative, AFK and Bad Manners banners?

That way they could see that they are doing the wrong actions in game and will work towards achieving those sexy teamwork banners. Leaver busters just give people more time to make a coffee/tea, go to the toilet, grab a feed, have a smoke or get another beer.

{{champion:83}}
